name: Honour The Old Comics
description:
discover universe series #7 : Arrived near the island after flying far from the indian ocean. Stop by to see a large place in the middle of the island of Java, made of many stones and carved stories. Where to store the story of the old kingdom's past. Seemed to greet the elder and greeted him warmly. Talk about our unique journey. In the end this journey doesn't just stop there, it's just a temporary break for something bigger.
